high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the white rubber spatula.
Take the spatula to the sink.
Set the spatula in the sink. Turn the water on in the sink. Turn the water off, let it drain out.
Take the spatula from the sink
Place the spatula in the wooden drawer to the left. Close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Take the spatula, rubber, from the countertop to the sink, rinse it,  put it in the drawer to the left of the sink.

high_descs: walk forwards a bit and then hang a left, walk to the end of the room and approach the kitchen counter on your right at the end of the room
grab a spatula off of the counter to the left of the pepper grinder
turn left and walk until you reach the sink on the right
place the spatula in the sink and clean it off, then pick it back up
turn left to face the cabinets
place the spatula in the pull out drawer in the corner of the cabinets on the right
anns.task_desc: place a clean spatula inside of the pullout drawer in the corner of the kitchen

high_descs: Turn left and go towards the oven.
Pick up the spatula that is on the counter between the oven and the grinder.
Go left and walk to the sink on the right hand side.
Put the spatula in to sink, turn on the water, and clean it.
Remove the spatula from the sink.
Open the drawer located to the left of the sink and place the clean spatula inside. Close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spatula into the correct drawer.
